reviewText: This made an amazing christmas gift for my father. He loves mike holmes and he has already seen these episodes but he can now watch it over and over when its not on tv, which has been alot lately! It was the best gift idea i came up with. I got it very fast with my prime shipping and it was brand new in the package, just as it said in the listing. Makes a great gift!!!

Four episodes from the 5 season series.

Contains: Kitchen Catastrophe, Tiles and Tribulations, Hell's Kitchen, & Cabinet Chaos.

Wish there was more
Mike Holmes is my "learn how to do it right" DIY hero.
